{"tid":2045724,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麻友 88","createTime":"2020-06-01T03:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T19:03:31.000Z","uid":1984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e39107e2ac61e947bebfaebd885f15537782d3","tid":2045724,"uid":1984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"前AKB48人氣成員渡邊麻友今天透過經紀公司發表聲明，宣布因為個人健康因素退出演藝圈。"},{"pid":"2af6ecf76a97da3bccdf26589877081b0a36e0de","tid":2045724,"uid":107231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3ec13f839f1e88aeb070c518e50190b7b602df","tid":2045724,"uid":107231,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:39:39.000Z","msg":"前AKB48人氣成員渡邊麻友今天透過經紀公司發表聲明，宣布因為個人健康因素退出演藝圈。經紀公司表示渡邊麻友的身體狀況已經無法繼續待在演藝圈活動，經過多次討論後，以她的意願為優先，因此決定結束合約，其演藝生涯也劃下句點。<br />\n<br />\n渡邊麻友於2006年12月加入AKB48，當年她才國中一年級，被粉絲們稱為「神7」之一（受到神眷顧的七人），2014年也成登上AKB48總選舉第一名，從團體畢業後，她努力朝向多方發展，挑戰音樂劇和連續劇演出，出道至今幾乎零緋聞，沒想到竟然因為身體健康因素而退出演藝圈，讓許多粉絲相當不捨。<br />\n<br />\n這也是繼昨天w-inds.緒方龍一之後，再度有日本藝人因為健康因素決定離開演藝圈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%9F%E5%A0%B1%E5%89%8D-akb-48-%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E6%B8%A1%E9%82%8A%E9%BA%BB%E5%8F%8B%E5%9B%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%8B%80%E6%B3%81%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E6%BC%94%E8%97%9D%E5%9C%88-031711539.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%259F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2589%258D-akb-48-%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E9%2582%258A%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E7%258B%2580%25E6%25B3%2581%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25BC%2594%25E8%2597%259D%25E5%259C%2588-031711539.html&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGlQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=0d3f2b51\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%